                                                <div class="starEmptySvg"><svg class="SvgIcon rfSvg rating"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8.005 8.198L.215 9.331a.25.25 0 0 0-.139.425l5.637 5.496-1.33 7.759a.25.25 0 0 0 .362.263l6.968-3.663 6.968 3.663a.25.25 0 0 0 .363-.263l-1.33-7.76 5.636-5.495a.25.25 0 0 0-.138-.425l-7.79-1.133-3.485-7.059a.25.25 0 0 0-.448 0L8.005 8.2" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></svg></div>
                                                <div class="starEmptySvg"><svg class="SvgIcon rfSvg rating"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M8.005 8.198L.215 9.331a.25.25 0 0 0-.139.425l5.637 5.496-1.33 7.759a.25.25 0 0 0 .362.263l6.968-3.663 6.968 3.663a.25.25 0 0 0 .363-.263l-1.33-7.76 5.636-5.495a.25.25 0 0 0-.138-.425l-7.79-1.133-3.485-7.059a.25.25 0 0 0-.448 0L8.005 8.2" fill-rule="evenodd"></path></svg></svg></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-person-detail">
                                <div class="text">Pauline vous conseille afin de présenter une offre compétitive.</div>
                                <div class="group-tel-btn">
                                    <div class="group-tel-btn__left">
                                        <a href="" class="btn btn-email">Par Email</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="group-tel-btn_right">
                                        <a href="" class="number-tel">+33 6 33 17 31 18</a>

                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="comissions">
                        Seulement <span class="highlight">5 000 €</span> de comissions fixes avec un agent EZI-X
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>


</div>

